originalText.text:
If you want your car consistently damaged, park here.
This garage is usually overbooked. Space is very tight.
And there is also a rude manager, on duty for most the the day shifts. He abuses the cars, speeding and slamming on the breaks in a usually packed garage. He also requires a 3 hour notice for the car to be pulled. If you ask for your car 2 hours in advance you need to find alternative transportation. He is also a money grubber. Asked me for $50 cash when I signed up for my monthly garage.
